{"tid":576264,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺寵物店嘅人特別乞人憎？","createTime":"2018-02-28T18:02:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T06:00:07.000Z","uid":91835,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c4f5df2b962ad162f203919d9d5ab331d47e69a4","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:02:35.000Z","msg":"寵物店裏面一格格箱未通常寫住「不准拍打」嘅，咁我明白因為好多時啲箱都係用玻璃做，同埋怕嚇親小動物<br />\n<br />\n但我見好多時啲貓貓狗狗係個箱入邊悶到根本好似抑鬱咁，瞓喺度又目光呆滯，其實隔住塊玻璃撩佢玩有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n本人其實有意買寵物嘅，所以今日去金魚街行左一趟，見到啲貓貓狗狗（尤其是狗）好似等死咁瞓晒係個箱入面，未撩佢玩下<br />\n<br />\n跟住隻狗玩到好high，不停咁跳黎跳去好興奮咁，仲要露齒笑，呢個時候個職員閪撚晒面：「唔好伸手啦唔該！」我又唔係拍打玻璃，只係隔住玻璃同隻狗玩，我都見佢好似好開心好興奮咁<br />\n<br />\n啲寵物店職員懶係好似好有愛心咁，但其實諗緊，你買就買，唔買就過主啦，唔好掂我啲貨物<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9549d37765b8ff594a6bc9dac55af8552ef23622","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"一諗到呢點就好嬲，其實隻狗仔日日俾人困住喺度，不知幾想有人同佢玩關心佢，你啲仆街寵物店職員淨係識攞佢哋黎搵錢，見到有人行近少少就閪撚哂面<br />\n<br />\n冇錯呀今次又係旺角金魚街"},{"pid":"a82e951ab92634a1ed4d89af14fcf574a07326cd","tid":576264,"uid":161709,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"有意買寵物<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e934f7ca9a2995f1129af3798b7c3e9394070dc8","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"a82e951ab92634a1ed4d89af14fcf574a07326cd","tid":576264,"uid":161709,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"有意買寵物<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"領養手續繁複嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知衰啦"},{"pid":"2f1342e2de0a26e0b4f6aa5bd035f5fe75ceea4c","tid":576264,"uid":27793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"我以前中學時代做pt<br />\n就算人工幾低<br />\n我都笑住對客 笑住講唔好意思唔可以bla bla bla<br />\n<br />\n可能寵物店真係太低人工 只係請到啲mk<br />\nmk唔會講修養同脾氣"},{"pid":"3f9d0f8b2614f514c72f16c45b84db1c33d7f6a2","tid":576264,"uid":117722,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"買寵物已經on9<br />\n人地鋪頭入貨就係應酬你呢D垃圾"},{"pid":"a940633917b94dde232b007afe529ba50eee8033","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f1342e2de0a26e0b4f6aa5bd035f5fe75ceea4c","tid":576264,"uid":27793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:15:49.000Z","msg":"我以前中學時代做pt<br />\n就算人工幾低<br />\n我都笑住對客 笑住講唔好意思唔可以bla bla bla<br />\n<br />\n可能寵物店真係太低人工 只係請到啲mk<br />\nmk唔會講修養同脾氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:17:38.000Z","msg":"讀唔成書都算，終於要對啲客同寵物態度都咁差"},{"pid":"a59856da7c993931f39cbc5d10bd02acf982acca","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"3f9d0f8b2614f514c72f16c45b84db1c33d7f6a2","tid":576264,"uid":117722,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:17:30.000Z","msg":"買寵物已經on9<br />\n人地鋪頭入貨就係應酬你呢D垃圾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:18:37.000Z","msg":"我冇幫襯佢哋囉，就算幫襯都唔會幫襯金魚街啲黑店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 純粹行過入去價下格"},{"pid":"3b32a05431a348532b3532bb95a72a23b7653ec0","tid":576264,"uid":137261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"格價咁你同話佢地當寵物係貨品有分別咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4af7fefe161547f99b7160a19fc854153190c4d","tid":576264,"uid":706,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e934f7ca9a2995f1129af3798b7c3e9394070dc8","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"a82e951ab92634a1ed4d89af14fcf574a07326cd","tid":576264,"uid":161709,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"有意買寵物<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:12:18.000Z","msg":"領養手續繁複嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我知衰啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:21:05.000Z","msg":"講撚到自己幾咁有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知仲撚衰<br />\n收皮啦你"},{"pid":"3d2eef52f1a434c21f99e8b46774d422244eefaf","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:25:24.000Z","msg":"都話我知衰囉，同埋我都冇諗住幫襯金魚街<br />\n連登仔又贏一仗，個個都企係道德高地，從來唔買寵物，只會領養同拯救被遺棄孤兒，高尚品德惹人稱讚！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d397bceb64cbdd068626ccd39de3cc98af7878b9","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3b32a05431a348532b3532bb95a72a23b7653ec0","tid":576264,"uid":137261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:21:04.000Z","msg":"格價咁你同話佢地當寵物係貨品有分別咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:01.000Z","msg":"格價唔可以係格寵物用品架？<br />\n我知連登仔個個愛心爆棚，絕對唔會買寵物嘅！屋企啲貓貓狗狗一係係街執返嚟，一係人哋送嘅，絕對唔會係寵物店買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a201595afe36b608cbebdfe13eefc52f06fc19","tid":576264,"uid":58165,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"領養撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f055e788f668693d3b55ea6e1b3d96e0a3116068","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a201595afe36b608cbebdfe13eefc52f06fc19","tid":576264,"uid":58165,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"領養撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db99ef0a1c13c34eb515ad639edbafdb50372894","tid":576264,"uid":21175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f055e788f668693d3b55ea6e1b3d96e0a3116068","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a201595afe36b608cbebdfe13eefc52f06fc19","tid":576264,"uid":58165,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"領養撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"其實如果真係買寵物應該要去邊到買？"},{"pid":"cb77cd47e37a6dcd3d910ca6210fb0574112ef40","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db99ef0a1c13c34eb515ad639edbafdb50372894","tid":576264,"uid":21175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f055e788f668693d3b55ea6e1b3d96e0a3116068","tid":576264,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49a201595afe36b608cbebdfe13eefc52f06fc19","tid":576264,"uid":58165,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:32.000Z","msg":"領養撚全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:31:11.000Z","msg":"其實如果真係買寵物應該要去邊到買？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"如果你唔怕煩嘅當然領養係最好啦<br />\n但如果想直接買嘅上網搵下資料先囉，金魚街大部份都係黑店黎"},{"pid":"754d0d3d82a52cf3e07abaa97521da160f876428","tid":576264,"uid":98273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:47:22.000Z","msg":"金魚街果啲好多黑店 試過有隻狗仔流哂鼻水 個店員話佢緊張姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要去就去勝利道果邊 多啲睇 都有黑店都有伏 睇你好冇彩<br />\n<br />\n利申一隻領養兩隻買"},{"pid":"f0f89b8d6114628d0bbed13733c12370503defac","tid":576264,"uid":144660,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"根本唔係唔想領養 係大部份寵物義工都臭西黎<br />\n要番工又話我冇時間照顧 唔洗番工又話我冇錢<br />\n住私樓又話未必養得狗 講撚到明可以養狗又話你屋企冇位比佢跑<br />\n一係你就一早打定二三千呎既豪宅先養得啦屌<br />\n跟住班領養撚又會叫你去邊度邊度領養 然後自己個隻原來買番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"314886e3eff0bc7905bf98bdc16a95e0d0e7d0f1","tid":576264,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"狗唔係人<br />\n你玩完行返出街就收復心情<br />\n狗唔係，需要更長嘅時間去平復<br />\n<br />\n加上個籠又唔係大，一陣整親狗又好人又好都唔知入邊個數<br />\n<br />\n你咁同行入七仔拎起包朱古力揸住廿分鐘又放返上架冇分別<br />\n眼看手勿動好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac4c3dde51a4d36ef85be29655d5ddf80e22610","tid":576264,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"金魚街買寵物你戇鳩架?<br />\n你老母企金魚缸?<br />\n咁撚鍾意金魚<br />\n<br />\n要買都咪撚係金魚街買喇"},{"pid":"2ebce463de246586114f892b911372579fe71ae9","tid":576264,"uid":110964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a82e951ab92634a1ed4d89af14fcf574a07326cd","tid":576264,"uid":161709,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T18:10:27.000Z","msg":"有意買寵物<br />\n<br />\n垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:46:41.000Z","msg":"我想養雪橇bb，邊到有得領養？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：屋企過萬呎，可以養狗，長開冷暖恆溫，有工人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de4f8ec0a29ed8b897e2f696d32b434ba9f8efb","tid":576264,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"唔攪老闆攪人店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主膽識過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲好識做好事<br />\n雖然唔知做過啲咩"},{"pid":"30de1a35ddf176cb79e5ea659dc20405c66aae13","tid":576264,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"因為有啲00後 支那人<br />\n真係好撚鐘意大大力拍鳩塊玻璃 好無教養<br />\n當然樓主個情況 我覺得無問題"},{"pid":"16aa2d5aa9845f40049a38a70ae370aecaa9fdd3","tid":576264,"uid":1993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T06:00:07.000Z","msg":"戇鳩開得舖頭就係要賺錢<br />\n咁有愛心把撚呀？<br />\n係買嘅人助長"}]}